<section class="challenges-section">
<div class="container">
<h2>Construction Industry Challenges</h2>
<p class="section-intro">The construction industry faces unique challenges. We help contractors build stronger, more profitable businesses.</p>
<div class="challenges-grid">
<div class="challenge-card">
<h3>Cash Flow Issues</h3>
<ul>
<li>Slow payment cycles</li>
<li>Retention holdbacks</li>
<li>Front-loaded expenses</li>
<li>Change order delays</li>
<li>Progress billing problems</li>
<li>Seasonal fluctuations</li>
</ul>
<p class="solution"><strong>Our Solution:</strong> Cash flow management systems improving working capital by 40-60%.</p>
</div>
<div class="challenge-card">
<h3>Project Profitability</h3>
<ul>
<li>Inaccurate estimates</li>
<li>Cost overruns</li>
<li>Poor job costing</li>
<li>Scope creep</li>
<li>Inefficient operations</li>
<li>Low margins</li>
</ul>
<p class="solution"><strong>Our Solution:</strong> Project management improvements increasing margins 5-10 percentage points.</p>
</div>
<div class="challenge-card">
<h3>Business Growth</h3>
<ul>
<li>Bonding limitations</li>
<li>Skilled labor shortage</li>
<li>Equipment costs</li>
<li>Market competition</li>
<li>Scalability issues</li>
<li>Succession planning</li>
</ul>
<p class="solution"><strong>Our Solution:</strong> Strategic growth planning doubling bonding capacity and revenue in 2-3 years.</p>
</div>
<div class="challenge-card">
<h3>Risk Management</h3>
<ul>
<li>Contract disputes</li>
<li>Safety compliance</li>
<li>Insurance costs</li>
<li>Warranty claims</li>
<li>Subcontractor issues</li>
<li>Legal exposure</li>
</ul>
<p class="solution"><strong>Our Solution:</strong> Risk mitigation strategies reducing claims 50% and insurance costs 20-30%.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
