<!-- Case Study Section -->
<section class="case-study-preview">
<div class="container">
<h2>Construction Success Story</h2>
<div class="case-study-card">
<h3>Commercial General Contractor - Rhode Island</h3>
<div class="case-details">
<div class="challenge">
<h4>Challenge:</h4>
<p>$25M GC with 3% net margins, cash flow problems, $10M bonding limit, 15% project overruns, struggling to grow beyond current size.</p>
</div>
<div class="solution">
<h4>Our Solution:</h4>
<ul>
<li>Implemented integrated project management and accounting system</li>
<li>Developed accurate estimating and job costing procedures</li>
<li>Created cash flow management and billing processes</li>
<li>Improved financial reporting for bonding company</li>
<li>Established project controls and change management</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="results">
<h4>Results (18 months):</h4>
<div class="result-metrics">
<span><strong>$38M</strong> Revenue</span>
<span><strong>7.2%</strong> Net Margins</span>
<span><strong>$25M</strong> Bonding Capacity</span>
<span><strong>5%</strong> Average Overruns</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>

